# Unicode.GeneralCategory.modifierSymbol

**Case**

A non-letterlike modifier symbol.

## Declaration

```swift
case modifierSymbol
```

## Discussion

This value corresponds to the category `Modifier_Symbol` (abbreviated `Sk`) in the [https://unicode.org/reports/tr44/#General_Category_Values].
